DISCIPLINARY DOCKET

96-985. Disciplinary Counsel v. Mazer.

This matter is pending before the court upon the filing by respondent on February 15, 2001, of a motion for leave. Upon consideration thereof,

IT IS HEREBY ORDERED that the motion be, and hereby is, granted and that respondent may file a reply to relator’s response on or before ten days from the date of this order.
